## Future Architecture (Scale Stage — 100k+ users)

When API costs outgrow revenue, the move is:

```
User → Frontend → Backend → Fine-tuned Llama 3 (self-hosted on GPU server)
                                    ↑
                        Trained on synthetic data (GPT-4 generated)
                        + real user map data collected over time
                        Hosted on RunPod or AWS GPU instance
                        ~$200-500/month flat vs $10k+/month on API
```

**How to get training data when you have none:**

1. Use GPT-4 or Claude to generate 500+ high quality Fractal maps synthetically
1. Review and curate the good ones
1. Launch on Groq API and collect real user maps + engagement signals
1. Combine synthetic + real data → fine-tune Llama 3
1. Self-host the fine-tuned model → costs drop dramatically

